  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nUAF bug in blink, it affects chromium from version 85 to 89.  \nThe problem is:  \nOn CanvasRenderingContext2D constuctor, which hold a raw pointer ukm_recorder_ which will be freed on the Document destruct.  \nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/refs/tags/8"
